OL,3,C'My joy's gone': Mum of teen killed in
OL,4,Ccar crash calls for licence change
OL,6,FShe told ITV News: "My passion for
OL,7,Feverything has gone, my joy for
OL,8,Feverything is gone.
OL,10,F"So it's actually really hard to get
OL,11,Fback to life before Harvey".
OL,13,F"How do you sum up somebody that's
OL,14,Fjust so perfect? Basically, he was
OL,15,Fabsolutely, like, just the most
OL,16,Flovable person you could ever meet.
OL,18,F"He was, he's just absolutely
OL,19,Fbeautiful person".
