OL,3,C'My joy's gone': Mum of teen killed in
OL,4,Ccar crash calls for licence change
OL,6,FMs Owen recalls to ITV News the panic
OL,7,Fthat she was in the night that Harvey
OL,8,Fdied.
OL,10,F"So after like, a night of no sleep,
OL,11,Fwe sat off really early hours and
OL,12,Fjust, I was just driving namelessly
OL,13,Faround Snowdon, you just don't know,
OL,14,Fabsolute blind panic and, and then it
OL,15,Fhit me that the vastness of the place
OL,16,Fand and that's when, like, the panic
OL,17,Fstarted to kick in.
