OL,3,C'My joy's gone': Mum of teen killed in
OL,4,Ccar crash calls for licence change
OL,6,F"But the whole time, I just kept
OL,7,Fthinking that they wondered off and
OL,8,Fthey were lost. When I got to the
OL,9,Fpolice station and we found that
OL,10,Fthey'd found a car in the ditch.
OL,12,F"And even then, I just kept thinking,
OL,13,Fyou know, they would have wondered
OL,14,Foff, they'd be fine.
OL,16,F"And then it was some time until we
OL,17,Fwere told and and then it was all just
OL,18,Fa blur from the number".
OL,20,FMs Owen wants a new law for young
OL,21,Fdrivers called a graduated licence.
