OL,3,C'My joy's gone': Mum of teen killed in
OL,4,Ccar crash calls for licence change
OL,6,FShe had started a petition to change
OL,7,Fthe law around licences that had made
OL,8,Fit all the way to parliament.
OL,10,FBut now there is a new government, so
OL,11,Fshe has to start the petition all over
OL,12,Fagain. All this while dealing with the
OL,13,Fdeath of her son and the ongoing
OL,14,Finquest into his death in Wales.
